                    Simple Admin Dashboard for managing your library inventory. Track books, organize categories, and manage authors all in one place.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <img src="https://plus.unsplash.com/premium_photo-1677567996070-68fa4181775a?q=80&w=1172&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" class="img-fluid rounded-end-4 h-100 object-fit-cover" alt="Library Shelves">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>